 414:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\drivers/peripheral/sysclk/cy_sysclk.h **** *   connection and chip-specific destination on the device.
 415:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\drivers/peripheral/sysclk/cy_sysclk.h **** *
